        How to Negotiate a Real Estate Agent's Commission in Queensland
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Commissions are negotiable in Queensland. But negotiating for the lowest rate is not always the smartest move. Here's how to think about it properly.
      </p>
